{"title":"在hexo博客中创建一个简单的相册","slug":"2019101502","date":"2019-10-15T02:16:23.000Z","updated":"2019-10-17T14:09:49.000Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/2019101502.json","excerpt":"之前就有着给自己的博客里添加一个相册的想法，因为时间比较紧张，才一直拖到了现在，因为目前来说，图片只有在相册这种形式下才可以更好的留存，如果只是单纯的发一篇日志，并不能将图片很好的展现出来，所以我才决定要做这个相册的。","covers":["http://th0923.xyz//image/%E6%B7%B1%E5%BA%A6%E6%88%AA%E5%9B%BE_%E9%80%89%E6%8B%A9%E5%8C%BA%E5%9F%9F_20191015224109.png"],"content":"<p>之前就有着给自己的博客里添加一个相册的想法，因为时间比较紧张，才一直拖到了现在，因为目前来说，图片只有在相册这种形式下才可以更好的留存，如果只是单纯的发一篇日志，并不能将图片很好的展现出来，所以我才决定要做这个相册的。<a id=\"more\"></a><br><img src=\"http://th0923.xyz//image/%E6%B7%B1%E5%BA%A6%E6%88%AA%E5%9B%BE_%E9%80%89%E6%8B%A9%E5%8C%BA%E5%9F%9F_20191015224109.png\"><br>在做这个相册之前有查找过很多方法，但是大多都是将图片直接存在博客里，或者github中，我认为这样首先会加大服务器的压力，同时github的访问速度还会很慢，而我最想要的效果应该是这个相册是可以结合自己的图床使用的，所以我在结合他人方法的同时也进行了自己的方法的修改。</p>\n<h2 id=\"找图床\"><a href=\"#找图床\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"找图床\"></a>找图床</h2><p>国内来说，图床的选择还是很多，我之前主要在用的是<a href=\"https://www.superbed.cn/\">聚合图床</a>，这个图床的优点很明显，就是上传方便，免费，同时可以自动将你的图片分发到多家图片服务器上去，防止图床崩掉而造成的一系列问题，但是也有自己的缺点，别的不说，这个东西毕竟是别人家的！你永远不知道下一秒这个服务器会不会崩掉。其次，不便于管理也是我认为这个图床平台的弊端之一。相册里的图片本就应该是很珍贵的，可能每一张图片的丢失都会让你很遗憾，所以这种情况下我们不得不搭建一个自己的图床（对象存储服务器），其实很简单，而这样的选择就比较明确了，腾讯云，阿里云等等。而我个人最后用的七牛云，其实只是七牛云的资费很便宜，拥有10个G的免费流量（不是内存）。具体图床的搭建我会在后期再写一篇博客的。</p>\n<h2 id=\"新建相册页面\"><a href=\"#新建相册页面\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"新建相册页面\"></a>新建相册页面</h2><p>首先进入博客的根目录下新建一个页面。</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">hexo new page photos</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>在<strong>主题配置文件中</strong>将他添加到主页的菜单中</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">menu:</span><br><span class=\"line\">  photos: &#x2F;photos || camera-retro</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>菜单的文字默认是photos（英文），如果需要记得去zh-Hans中汉化。</p>\n<p>修改source/photos/index.md文件</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">---</span><br><span class=\"line\">title: 相册</span><br><span class=\"line\">type: picture</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">---</span><br><span class=\"line\">&lt;div class&#x3D;&quot;ImageGrid&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;div&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>其中title可以任意的更换，type因为在后面的swig中有用到，如果要更换一定要在swig中也要换掉。</p>\n<h2 id=\"准备图片列表\"><a href=\"#准备图片列表\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"准备图片列表\"></a>准备图片列表</h2><p>这里参考了其他的方法，他们大多是将图片放在一个文件夹里，然后将这个文件夹里的图片自动整理出一份列表保存成json数组。因为我要使用网络url，所以便要自己整理出一份列表，以后每次只要在这个列表里增加url即可。<br>在source/photos/新建一个文件<strong>photoslist.json</strong>,并向其中添加数据，格式如下：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">[</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        &quot;title&quot;:&quot;故宫&quot;,</span><br><span class=\"line\">        &quot;url&quot;:&quot;http:&#x2F;&#x2F;th0923.xyz&#x2F;photos&#x2F;62aad664gy1g7hurc90gcj21900u0b29.jpg&quot;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;,    </span><br><span class=\"line\">&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        &quot;title&quot;:&quot;1到30题封面&quot;,</span><br><span class=\"line\">        &quot;url&quot;:&quot;http:&#x2F;&#x2F;th0923.xyz&#x2F;image&#x2F;%E7%AE%97%E6%B3%95%E9%A2%98%E9%80%9A%E7%94%A830.png&quot;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;,</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        &quot;title&quot;:&quot;看海&quot;,</span><br><span class=\"line\">        &quot;url&quot;:&quot;http:&#x2F;&#x2F;th0923.xyz&#x2F;photos&#x2F;%E5%BE%AE%E4%BF%A1%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%87_20190906092117.jpg&quot;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">]</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>其中title你可以为这张照片起名，也可以为空，url即代表图片的链接。</p>\n<h2 id=\"导入所需文件\"><a href=\"#导入所需文件\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"导入所需文件\"></a>导入所需文件</h2><ol>\n<li>photo.js<br>该文件主要用于解读之前的图片列表，并将他们拼成网页填充到之前的index.md中，需要导入到source/js目录下，如没有该目录需手动新建，文件内容如下：<figure class=\"highlight javascript\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br><span class=\"line\">19</span><br><span class=\"line\">20</span><br><span class=\"line\">21</span><br><span class=\"line\">22</span><br><span class=\"line\">23</span><br><span class=\"line\">24</span><br><span class=\"line\">25</span><br><span class=\"line\">26</span><br><span class=\"line\">27</span><br><span class=\"line\">28</span><br><span class=\"line\">29</span><br><span class=\"line\">30</span><br><span class=\"line\">31</span><br><span class=\"line\">32</span><br><span class=\"line\">33</span><br><span class=\"line\">34</span><br><span class=\"line\">35</span><br><span class=\"line\">36</span><br><span class=\"line\">37</span><br><span class=\"line\">38</span><br><span class=\"line\">39</span><br><span class=\"line\">40</span><br><span class=\"line\">41</span><br><span class=\"line\">42</span><br><span class=\"line\">43</span><br><span class=\"line\">44</span><br><span class=\"line\">45</span><br><span class=\"line\">46</span><br><span class=\"line\">47</span><br><span class=\"line\">48</span><br><span class=\"line\">49</span><br><span class=\"line\">50</span><br><span class=\"line\">51</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">photo =&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    page: <span class=\"number\">1</span>,</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"comment\">//offset 用于设置照片数量的上限</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    offset: <span class=\"number\">100</span>,</span><br><span class=\"line\">    init: <span class=\"function\"><span class=\"keyword\">function</span> (<span class=\"params\"></span>) </span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">var</span> that = <span class=\"built_in\">this</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"comment\">//这里设置的是刚才生成的 json 文件路径</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        $.getJSON(<span class=\"string\">&quot;/photos/photoslist.json&quot;</span>, <span class=\"function\"><span class=\"keyword\">function</span> (<span class=\"params\">data</span>) </span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            that.render(that.page, data);</span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"comment\">//that.scroll(data);</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        &#125;);</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;,</span><br><span class=\"line\">    render: <span class=\"function\"><span class=\"keyword\">function</span> (<span class=\"params\">page, data</span>) </span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">var</span> begin = (page - <span class=\"number\">1</span>) * <span class=\"built_in\">this</span>.offset;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">var</span> end = page * <span class=\"built_in\">this</span>.offset;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">if</span> (begin &gt;= data.length) <span class=\"keyword\">return</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">var</span> html, imgNameWithPattern, imgName, imageSize, imageX, imageY, li = <span class=\"string\">&quot;&quot;</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">for</span> (<span class=\"keyword\">var</span> i = begin; i &lt; end &amp;&amp; i &lt; data.length; i++) &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">           imgNameWithPattern = data[i].url;</span><br><span class=\"line\">           imgName = data[i].title</span><br><span class=\"line\">           <span class=\"comment\">//这里 250 指的是图片的宽度，可以根据自己的需要调整相册中照片的大小</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">            li += <span class=\"string\">&#x27;&lt;div class=&quot;card&quot; style=&quot;width:250px&quot;&gt;&#x27;</span> +</span><br><span class=\"line\">                    <span class=\"string\">&#x27;&lt;div class=&quot;ImageInCard&quot; style=&quot;height:&#x27;</span>+ <span class=\"number\">250</span>  + <span class=\"string\">&#x27;px&quot;&gt;&#x27;</span> +</span><br><span class=\"line\">                    <span class=\"comment\">//href 和 src 的链接地址是相册照片外部链接，也可以放博客目录里</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">                      <span class=\"string\">&#x27;&lt;a data-fancybox=&quot;gallery&quot; href=&quot;&#x27;</span> + imgNameWithPattern + <span class=\"string\">&#x27;?raw=true&quot; data-caption=&quot;&#x27;</span> + imgName + <span class=\"string\">&#x27;&quot;&gt;&#x27;</span> +</span><br><span class=\"line\">                <span class=\"comment\">//注意:该处的srcset我在url后加了-toSmall，这是我在七牛云写好的一个样式</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">                <span class=\"comment\">//样式具体的使用方法大家请自行百度，</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">                <span class=\"comment\">//这里主要用于自动缩略图，不需要的可以delete掉</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">                        <span class=\"string\">&#x27;&lt;img class=&quot;CpicView&quot; srcset=&quot;&#x27;</span> + imgNameWithPattern + <span class=\"string\">&#x27;-toSmall?raw=true&quot; src=&quot;&#x27;</span> + imgNameWithPattern + <span class=\"string\">&#x27;?raw=true&quot;/&gt;&#x27;</span> +</span><br><span class=\"line\">                      <span class=\"string\">&#x27;&lt;/a&gt;&#x27;</span> +</span><br><span class=\"line\">                    <span class=\"string\">&#x27;&lt;/div&gt;&#x27;</span> +</span><br><span class=\"line\">                    <span class=\"comment\">// &#x27;&lt;div class=&quot;TextInCard&quot;&gt;&#x27; + imgName + &#x27;&lt;/div&gt;&#x27; +  //图片下显示文件名作为说明的功能</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">                  <span class=\"string\">&#x27;&lt;/div&gt;&#x27;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        $(<span class=\"string\">&quot;.ImageGrid&quot;</span>).append(li);</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"comment\">//$(&quot;.ImageGrid&quot;).lazyload();</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"built_in\">this</span>.minigrid();</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;,</span><br><span class=\"line\">    minigrid: <span class=\"function\"><span class=\"keyword\">function</span>(<span class=\"params\"></span>) </span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">var</span> grid = <span class=\"keyword\">new</span> Minigrid(&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            container: <span class=\"string\">&#x27;.ImageGrid&#x27;</span>,</span><br><span class=\"line\">            item: <span class=\"string\">&#x27;.card&#x27;</span>,</span><br><span class=\"line\">            gutter: <span class=\"number\">12</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        &#125;);</span><br><span class=\"line\">        grid.mount();</span><br><span class=\"line\">        $(<span class=\"built_in\">window</span>).resize(<span class=\"function\"><span class=\"keyword\">function</span>(<span class=\"params\"></span>) </span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">           grid.mount();</span><br><span class=\"line\">        &#125;);</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">photo.init();</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li>\n<li>custom.styl<br>用于自定义样式，我使用的是next主题，该文件在主题里已经有了，自己修改就好，其他主题将以下样式想办法添加到自己的页面里就好。文件路径：themes/next/source/css/custom/_custom.styl<figure class=\"highlight css\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br><span class=\"line\">19</span><br><span class=\"line\">20</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">// Custom styles.</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"selector-class\">.ImageGrid</span> &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"attribute\">width</span>: <span class=\"number\">100%</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"attribute\">max-width</span>: <span class=\"number\">1040px</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"attribute\">margin</span>: <span class=\"number\">0</span> auto;</span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"attribute\">text-align</span>: center;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"selector-class\">.card</span> &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"attribute\">overflow</span>: hidden;</span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"attribute\">transition</span>: .<span class=\"number\">3s</span> ease-in-out;</span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"attribute\">border-radius</span>: <span class=\"number\">8px</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"attribute\">background-color</span>: <span class=\"number\">#ddd</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"selector-class\">.ImageInCard</span> <span class=\"selector-tag\">img</span> &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"attribute\">padding</span>: <span class=\"number\">0</span> <span class=\"number\">0</span> <span class=\"number\">0</span> <span class=\"number\">0</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"attribute\">border-radius</span>: <span class=\"number\">8px</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"selector-class\">.CpicView</span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"attribute\">width</span>:<span class=\"number\">100%</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li>\n<li>swig<br>直接将以下内如添加到页面的布局swig中即可，next主题的文件路径：themes/next/layout/_layout.swig<br>需要注意的是尽量添加到body标签的末尾，因为操作的本意是导入script包嘛。<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">&#123;% if page.type &#x3D;&#x3D;&#x3D;&#39;picture&#39; %&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">  &lt;script src&#x3D;&quot;&#x2F;&#x2F;cdn.jsdelivr.net&#x2F;npm&#x2F;minigrid@3.1.1&#x2F;dist&#x2F;minigrid.min.js&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;script&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">  &lt;script src&#x3D;&quot;&#x2F;js&#x2F;photo.js&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;script&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#123;% endif %&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h2 id=\"完成\"><a href=\"#完成\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"完成\"></a>完成</h2>以上配置结束后就完成所有的工作了，重新发布就能看到效果，如果你还想根据自己的喜好修改。</li>\n</ol>\n<ul>\n<li>改样式。直接在custom中修改样式即可</li>\n<li>改为本地图片。将图片保存在source/photos中，路径直接修改即可,如要自动生成列表，请参照其他教程</li>\n</ul>\n","more":"<br><img src=\"http://th0923.xyz//image/%E6%B7%B1%E5%BA%A6%E6%88%AA%E5%9B%BE_%E9%80%89%E6%8B%A9%E5%8C%BA%E5%9F%9F_20191015224109.png\"><br>在做这个相册之前有查找过很多方法，但是大多都是将图片直接存在博客里，或者github中，我认为这样首先会加大服务器的压力，同时github的访问速度还会很慢，而我最想要的效果应该是这个相册是可以结合自己的图床使用的，所以我在结合他人方法的同时也进行了自己的方法的修改。</p>\n<h2 id=\"找图床\"><a href=\"#找图床\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"找图床\"></a>找图床</h2><p>国内来说，图床的选择还是很多，我之前主要在用的是<a href=\"https://www.superbed.cn/\">聚合图床</a>，这个图床的优点很明显，就是上传方便，免费，同时可以自动将你的图片分发到多家图片服务器上去，防止图床崩掉而造成的一系列问题，但是也有自己的缺点，别的不说，这个东西毕竟是别人家的！你永远不知道下一秒这个服务器会不会崩掉。其次，不便于管理也是我认为这个图床平台的弊端之一。相册里的图片本就应该是很珍贵的，可能每一张图片的丢失都会让你很遗憾，所以这种情况下我们不得不搭建一个自己的图床（对象存储服务器），其实很简单，而这样的选择就比较明确了，腾讯云，阿里云等等。而我个人最后用的七牛云，其实只是七牛云的资费很便宜，拥有10个G的免费流量（不是内存）。具体图床的搭建我会在后期再写一篇博客的。</p>\n<h2 id=\"新建相册页面\"><a href=\"#新建相册页面\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"新建相册页面\"></a>新建相册页面</h2><p>首先进入博客的根目录下新建一个页面。</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">hexo new page photos</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>在<strong>主题配置文件中</strong>将他添加到主页的菜单中</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">menu:</span><br><span class=\"line\">  photos: &#x2F;photos || camera-retro</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>菜单的文字默认是photos（英文），如果需要记得去zh-Hans中汉化。</p>\n<p>修改source/photos/index.md文件</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">---</span><br><span class=\"line\">title: 相册</span><br><span class=\"line\">type: picture</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">---</span><br><span class=\"line\">&lt;div class&#x3D;&quot;ImageGrid&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;div&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>其中title可以任意的更换，type因为在后面的swig中有用到，如果要更换一定要在swig中也要换掉。</p>\n<h2 id=\"准备图片列表\"><a href=\"#准备图片列表\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"准备图片列表\"></a>准备图片列表</h2><p>这里参考了其他的方法，他们大多是将图片放在一个文件夹里，然后将这个文件夹里的图片自动整理出一份列表保存成json数组。因为我要使用网络url，所以便要自己整理出一份列表，以后每次只要在这个列表里增加url即可。<br>在source/photos/新建一个文件<strong>photoslist.json</strong>,并向其中添加数据，格式如下：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">[</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        &quot;title&quot;:&quot;故宫&quot;,</span><br><span class=\"line\">        &quot;url&quot;:&quot;http:&#x2F;&#x2F;th0923.xyz&#x2F;photos&#x2F;62aad664gy1g7hurc90gcj21900u0b29.jpg&quot;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;,    </span><br><span class=\"line\">&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        &quot;title&quot;:&quot;1到30题封面&quot;,</span><br><span class=\"line\">        &quot;url&quot;:&quot;http:&#x2F;&#x2F;th0923.xyz&#x2F;image&#x2F;%E7%AE%97%E6%B3%95%E9%A2%98%E9%80%9A%E7%94%A830.png&quot;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;,</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        &quot;title&quot;:&quot;看海&quot;,</span><br><span class=\"line\">        &quot;url&quot;:&quot;http:&#x2F;&#x2F;th0923.xyz&#x2F;photos&#x2F;%E5%BE%AE%E4%BF%A1%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%87_20190906092117.jpg&quot;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">]</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>其中title你可以为这张照片起名，也可以为空，url即代表图片的链接。</p>\n<h2 id=\"导入所需文件\"><a href=\"#导入所需文件\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"导入所需文件\"></a>导入所需文件</h2><ol>\n<li>photo.js<br>该文件主要用于解读之前的图片列表，并将他们拼成网页填充到之前的index.md中，需要导入到source/js目录下，如没有该目录需手动新建，文件内容如下：<figure class=\"highlight javascript\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br><span class=\"line\">19</span><br><span class=\"line\">20</span><br><span class=\"line\">21</span><br><span class=\"line\">22</span><br><span class=\"line\">23</span><br><span class=\"line\">24</span><br><span class=\"line\">25</span><br><span class=\"line\">26</span><br><span class=\"line\">27</span><br><span class=\"line\">28</span><br><span class=\"line\">29</span><br><span class=\"line\">30</span><br><span class=\"line\">31</span><br><span class=\"line\">32</span><br><span class=\"line\">33</span><br><span class=\"line\">34</span><br><span class=\"line\">35</span><br><span class=\"line\">36</span><br><span class=\"line\">37</span><br><span class=\"line\">38</span><br><span class=\"line\">39</span><br><span class=\"line\">40</span><br><span class=\"line\">41</span><br><span class=\"line\">42</span><br><span class=\"line\">43</span><br><span class=\"line\">44</span><br><span class=\"line\">45</span><br><span class=\"line\">46</span><br><span class=\"line\">47</span><br><span class=\"line\">48</span><br><span class=\"line\">49</span><br><span class=\"line\">50</span><br><span class=\"line\">51</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">photo =&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    page: <span class=\"number\">1</span>,</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"comment\">//offset 用于设置照片数量的上限</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    offset: <span class=\"number\">100</span>,</span><br><span class=\"line\">    init: <span class=\"function\"><span class=\"keyword\">function</span> (<span class=\"params\"></span>) </span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">var</span> that = <span class=\"built_in\">this</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"comment\">//这里设置的是刚才生成的 json 文件路径</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        $.getJSON(<span class=\"string\">&quot;/photos/photoslist.json&quot;</span>, <span class=\"function\"><span class=\"keyword\">function</span> (<span class=\"params\">data</span>) </span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            that.render(that.page, data);</span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"comment\">//that.scroll(data);</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        &#125;);</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;,</span><br><span class=\"line\">    render: <span class=\"function\"><span class=\"keyword\">function</span> (<span class=\"params\">page, data</span>) </span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">var</span> begin = (page - <span class=\"number\">1</span>) * <span class=\"built_in\">this</span>.offset;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">var</span> end = page * <span class=\"built_in\">this</span>.offset;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">if</span> (begin &gt;= data.length) <span class=\"keyword\">return</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">var</span> html, imgNameWithPattern, imgName, imageSize, imageX, imageY, li = <span class=\"string\">&quot;&quot;</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">for</span> (<span class=\"keyword\">var</span> i = begin; i &lt; end &amp;&amp; i &lt; data.length; i++) &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">           imgNameWithPattern = data[i].url;</span><br><span class=\"line\">           imgName = data[i].title</span><br><span class=\"line\">           <span class=\"comment\">//这里 250 指的是图片的宽度，可以根据自己的需要调整相册中照片的大小</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">            li += <span class=\"string\">&#x27;&lt;div class=&quot;card&quot; style=&quot;width:250px&quot;&gt;&#x27;</span> +</span><br><span class=\"line\">                    <span class=\"string\">&#x27;&lt;div class=&quot;ImageInCard&quot; style=&quot;height:&#x27;</span>+ <span class=\"number\">250</span>  + <span class=\"string\">&#x27;px&quot;&gt;&#x27;</span> +</span><br><span class=\"line\">                    <span class=\"comment\">//href 和 src 的链接地址是相册照片外部链接，也可以放博客目录里</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">                      <span class=\"string\">&#x27;&lt;a data-fancybox=&quot;gallery&quot; href=&quot;&#x27;</span> + imgNameWithPattern + <span class=\"string\">&#x27;?raw=true&quot; data-caption=&quot;&#x27;</span> + imgName + <span class=\"string\">&#x27;&quot;&gt;&#x27;</span> +</span><br><span class=\"line\">                <span class=\"comment\">//注意:该处的srcset我在url后加了-toSmall，这是我在七牛云写好的一个样式</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">                <span class=\"comment\">//样式具体的使用方法大家请自行百度，</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">                <span class=\"comment\">//这里主要用于自动缩略图，不需要的可以delete掉</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">                        <span class=\"string\">&#x27;&lt;img class=&quot;CpicView&quot; srcset=&quot;&#x27;</span> + imgNameWithPattern + <span class=\"string\">&#x27;-toSmall?raw=true&quot; src=&quot;&#x27;</span> + imgNameWithPattern + <span class=\"string\">&#x27;?raw=true&quot;/&gt;&#x27;</span> +</span><br><span class=\"line\">                      <span class=\"string\">&#x27;&lt;/a&gt;&#x27;</span> +</span><br><span class=\"line\">                    <span class=\"string\">&#x27;&lt;/div&gt;&#x27;</span> +</span><br><span class=\"line\">                    <span class=\"comment\">// &#x27;&lt;div class=&quot;TextInCard&quot;&gt;&#x27; + imgName + &#x27;&lt;/div&gt;&#x27; +  //图片下显示文件名作为说明的功能</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">                  <span class=\"string\">&#x27;&lt;/div&gt;&#x27;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        $(<span class=\"string\">&quot;.ImageGrid&quot;</span>).append(li);</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"comment\">//$(&quot;.ImageGrid&quot;).lazyload();</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"built_in\">this</span>.minigrid();</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;,</span><br><span class=\"line\">    minigrid: <span class=\"function\"><span class=\"keyword\">function</span>(<span class=\"params\"></span>) </span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">var</span> grid = <span class=\"keyword\">new</span> Minigrid(&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            container: <span class=\"string\">&#x27;.ImageGrid&#x27;</span>,</span><br><span class=\"line\">            item: <span class=\"string\">&#x27;.card&#x27;</span>,</span><br><span class=\"line\">            gutter: <span class=\"number\">12</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        &#125;);</span><br><span class=\"line\">        grid.mount();</span><br><span class=\"line\">        $(<span class=\"built_in\">window</span>).resize(<span class=\"function\"><span class=\"keyword\">function</span>(<span class=\"params\"></span>) </span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">           grid.mount();</span><br><span class=\"line\">        &#125;);</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">photo.init();</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li>\n<li>custom.styl<br>用于自定义样式，我使用的是next主题，该文件在主题里已经有了，自己修改就好，其他主题将以下样式想办法添加到自己的页面里就好。文件路径：themes/next/source/css/custom/_custom.styl<figure class=\"highlight css\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br><span class=\"line\">19</span><br><span class=\"line\">20</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">// Custom styles.</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"selector-class\">.ImageGrid</span> &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"attribute\">width</span>: <span class=\"number\">100%</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"attribute\">max-width</span>: <span class=\"number\">1040px</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"attribute\">margin</span>: <span class=\"number\">0</span> auto;</span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"attribute\">text-align</span>: center;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"selector-class\">.card</span> &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"attribute\">overflow</span>: hidden;</span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"attribute\">transition</span>: .<span class=\"number\">3s</span> ease-in-out;</span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"attribute\">border-radius</span>: <span class=\"number\">8px</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"attribute\">background-color</span>: <span class=\"number\">#ddd</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"selector-class\">.ImageInCard</span> <span class=\"selector-tag\">img</span> &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"attribute\">padding</span>: <span class=\"number\">0</span> <span class=\"number\">0</span> <span class=\"number\">0</span> <span class=\"number\">0</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"attribute\">border-radius</span>: <span class=\"number\">8px</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"selector-class\">.CpicView</span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"attribute\">width</span>:<span class=\"number\">100%</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li>\n<li>swig<br>直接将以下内如添加到页面的布局swig中即可，next主题的文件路径：themes/next/layout/_layout.swig<br>需要注意的是尽量添加到body标签的末尾，因为操作的本意是导入script包嘛。<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">&#123;% if page.type &#x3D;&#x3D;&#x3D;&#39;picture&#39; %&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">  &lt;script src&#x3D;&quot;&#x2F;&#x2F;cdn.jsdelivr.net&#x2F;npm&#x2F;minigrid@3.1.1&#x2F;dist&#x2F;minigrid.min.js&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;script&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">  &lt;script src&#x3D;&quot;&#x2F;js&#x2F;photo.js&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;script&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#123;% endif %&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h2 id=\"完成\"><a href=\"#完成\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"完成\"></a>完成</h2>以上配置结束后就完成所有的工作了，重新发布就能看到效果，如果你还想根据自己的喜好修改。</li>\n</ol>\n<ul>\n<li>改样式。直接在custom中修改样式即可</li>\n<li>改为本地图片。将图片保存在source/photos中，路径直接修改即可,如要自动生成列表，请参照其他教程</li>\n</ul>","categories":[{"name":"博客","path":"api/categories/博客.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"hexo","path":"api/tags/hexo.json"},{"name":"nexT主题","path":"api/tags/nexT主题.json"}]}